The article is a transcript of remarks made by Vice President Mike Pence at a life-issues luncheon. He thanks the Susan B. Anthony List for their work in supporting the pro-life movement and announces their partnership with the Life Issues Institute. Pence praises President Trump for his pro-life policies, including reinstating the Mexico City Policy, stopping funding of the United Nations Population Fund, and allowing states to defund Planned Parenthood. He encourages attendees to continue standing up and speaking out for the sanctity of life. Pence expresses confidence that the pro-life movement will restore the sanctity of life in America.